{
  "stem": "17308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, when I went back to Belgium after the war, when I came to know what was right and wrong, I wanted to make a court case to claim some damage just to have moral satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they-- they declared themself insolvent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Belgium lawyers-- if you claim any amount, whatever it is, so many percent you must pay to the government even if you get money.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But once they declare themself insolvent, there was no purpose to make any claim.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I made a moral claim, what I called one franc, what means nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's just a moral claim.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I couldn't do anything that means-- I couldn't get any satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Those people are still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They've got their business-- never mind where they declared insolvent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And whatever they could steal, they stole.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were surely other things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I know their name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I went to see them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They put a big act up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- and that's how far it went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And maybe if they would have played the game, my parents would have been alive today.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not in Luchon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Luchon was about a year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There it was a longer time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were quite incident.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was fighting incidents with fights with the German forces-- not exactly in the locality where I was, but in the area.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were quite-- periodically, I would say, there were incidents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a hilly area, forests, mountains there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were quite a number of hiding places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the German didn't like to go too far there, because they didn't, always, secure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then, incidents happened quite often.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Part only.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were some fatalities, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the German were leaving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Always, they-- they were not remaining.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the big area.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
